title: Model in a Bottle Original Makeup Setting Spray - 1.7 oz
description: Start your day with confidence with a few sprays of Model in a Bottle to lock in that perfect makeup look without the need for touchups. It's a one-of-a-kind matte finish setting spray. Model in a Bottle will hold foundation and eye makeup in place throughout the day and into the night. This product is resistant to smudging, tears, humidity and water. Indications Apply your make up as usual and allow your mascara to fully dry before applying. Close your eyes and spray evenly 10-12 inches from your face. Allow 20-30 seconds to dry before openning eyes.
